metry forbids mass and anomalous\nmagnetic dipole terms and in general admits six self-interaction terms. We\nconclude that this is the appropriate framework to attempt the incorporation of\nspin 1 matter bosons in chiral theories like the standard model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2013 10:43:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-05"}
