ally inactive galaxies by being depleted of HI gas and having no sign\nof star formation. Radio LINERs in the latter group are the best candidates for\nhosting low-luminosity radio AGN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2013 14:14:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
